          </li>
        </ul>

        <a
          href="#menu"
          class="btn-glow rounded-full bg-mango-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold text-white shadow-md shadow-mango-500/30 hover:bg-mango-600 sm:text-sm"
        >
          先選口味
        </a>
      </nav>

      <!-- Mobile nav -->
      <div class="border-t border-gray-100 md:hidden">
        <ul class="flex overflow-x-auto px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium whitespace-nowrap">
          <li><a href="#about" class="mr-4 text-gray-600">關於我們</a></li>
          <li><a href="#menu" class="mr-4 text-gray-600">果汁好物</a></li>
          <li><a href="#guide" class="mr-4 text-gray-600">觀光導覽</a></li>
          <li><a href="#reading" class="text-gray-600">水果讀物</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <!-- ========== Hero ========== -->
      <section
        class="hero-mesh relative overflow-hidden"
        aria-label="首頁橫幅"
      >
        <!-- Aurora + bubbles -->
        <div class="hero-aurora" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="bubble-field absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="bubble bubble--mango" style="--dur:9s;--delay:0s;--opacity:0.5;width:88px;height:88px;top:12%;left:6%;"></span>
          <span class="bubble bubble--mint" style="--dur:11s;--delay:1s;--opacity:0.45;width:56px;height:56px;top:28%;left:18%;"></span>
          <span class="bubble" style="--dur:8s;--delay:2s;--opacity:0.4;width:120px;height:120px;top:55%;left:4%;"></span>
          <span class="bubble bubble--mango" style="--dur:10s;--delay:0.5s;--opacity:0.55;width:72px;height:72px;top:18%;right:12%;"></span>
          <span class="bubble bubble--mint" style="--dur:12s;--delay:1.5s;--opacity:0.42;width:96px;height:96px;top:62%;right:8%;"></span>
          <span class="bubble" style="--dur:7s;--delay:3s;--opacity:0.35;width:44px;height:44px;top:78%;left:42%;"></span>
          <span class="bubble bubble--mango" style="--dur:9s;--delay:2.5s;--opacity:0.38;width:64px;height:64px;top:8%;left:48%;"></span>
        </div>

        <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24 lg:py-28">
          <div class="grid items-center gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="reveal-left">
              <span
                class="tech-pill mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-mint-600"
              >
                🌴 旗津在地 · 內行人的營養補充站
              </span>
              <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
                <strong class="bg-gradient-to-r from-mango-600 to-mango-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">旗津必吃</strong><br />
                <span class="gradient-heading">現打鮮果汁冰沙吧</span>
              </h1>
              <p class="mt-4 max-w-lg text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600 sm:text-lg">
                真水果、現點現打。手機選好亮給夥伴看，免排隊、快出杯。
                走<strong>旗津一日遊</strong>觀光路線會經過這裡，但很多遊客壓根不知道——當地居民、造船藍領、海科大的內行才會停。這杯<strong>高雄現打果汁</strong>，路過別就這樣走過去了。
              </p>
              <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <a
                  href="#menu"
                  class="btn-glow inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-mango-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-mango-500/30 hover:bg-mango-600"
                >
                  先看菜單
                  <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <a
                  href="#about"
                  class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border-2 border-gray-200 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 transition hover:border-mint-400 hover:text-mint-600"
                >
                  店怎麼走
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="reveal-right">
            <!-- Hero image placeholder -->
            <div
              class="image-placeholder-modern relative flex aspect-[4/3] flex-col items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-3xl"
              role="img"
              aria-label="店面形象圖片占位"
            >
              <svg class="mb-3 h-16 w-16 text-gray-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500">Hero 形象圖占位</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">替換為店面或果汁照片</p>
            </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="#about" class="scroll-hint mt-12 flex flex-col items-center gap-1 text-gray-400 no-underline" aria-label="往下滑動">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-medium tracking-widest uppercase">Scroll</span>
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ========== 1. About Us ========== -->
      <section id="about" class="section-bg section-bg-about scroll-mt-20 py-16 sm:py-24">
        <div class="tech-grid-layer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="section-inner mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6">
          <div class="reveal mb-12 text-left">
            <span class="section-badge tech-badge">About Us</span>
            <h2 class="section-title-tech mt-4">關於我們</h2>
            <div class="section-accent-line"></div>
            <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-gray-600">
              開了20年，就在觀光動線上。走旗津一日遊會經過，但你不知道——內行早就來買了。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid items-start gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="reveal-left space-y-6" style="--reveal-delay:0.1s">
              <div class="glass-card rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">開了20年，規矩沒變過</h3>
                <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
                  從2005年到現在，就一套：水果要熟、你點了才打、不多加糖騙人。
                  杯杯現做，喝到的就是水果本身，不是調味料調出來的。
                </p>
                <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
                  中洲三路641，距離渡輪站步行約3分鐘——<strong>旗津一日遊推薦</strong>路線幾乎都會經過這帶，但不少遊客就這樣走過去。
                  熟客是旗津當地居民、造船廠幹活的藍領、搭船過海來補體力的海科大學生；不用排隊、手機亮單、馬上出杯，這才是<strong>在地內行才知道</strong>的<strong>旗津必吃</strong>。
                </p>
                <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-mint-50 text-mint-500 text-xs">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">天亮去市場挑當季水果，熟透了才進店</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-mint-50 text-mint-500 text-xs">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">你點了才打，真材實料、不添加人工色素</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-mint-50 text-mint-500 text-xs">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">手機菜單選好、現場出示，即打即出杯，免排隊</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-mint-50 text-mint-500 text-xs">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">LINE Pay、街口支付，結帳也快</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Storefront image placeholder -->
            <div class="reveal-right space-y-4" style="--reveal-delay:0.2s">
              <div
                class="image-placeholder-modern relative flex aspect-[4/3] flex-col items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-3xl"
